snippet.title: Project BlockchainZ - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Download the prototype on itch.io: 
https://projectblockchainz.itch.io/project-blockchainz

Join the Official Discord Server:
http://www.projectbcz.com


Project BlockchainZ is a Third Person Shooter video game mixed with Real Time Tactics Mechanics in a post-apocalyptic world where the survival of the human kind depends on you.
